      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. u mentioned \"neat hair\" and \"minimal makeup.\" can u be a bit more specific on that? like, what kind of hair styles or grooming habits should they avoid if they want to make sure they aren't seen as too casual or unprofessional in a high-stakes environment?",
